762
00:33:21,999 --> 00:33:26,759
And as we were talking and going through this, I began to ask that individual, how do you

763
00:33:26,759 --> 00:33:29,639
think you could use that gift of exhortation?

764
00:33:29,639 --> 00:33:34,719
And we began to talk about some particular opportunities and some ways to use that gift.

765
00:33:34,719 --> 00:33:39,159
And then I walked them down in the basement, down to a bookshelf that has all kinds of

766
00:33:39,159 --> 00:33:40,159
cards on it.

767
00:33:40,159 --> 00:33:42,519
And I said, here are a bunch of cards.

768
00:33:42,519 --> 00:33:44,159
They're at your disposal.

769
00:33:44,159 --> 00:33:46,199
You use them as you'd like to.

770
00:33:46,199 --> 00:33:47,199
Why?

771
00:33:47,199 --> 00:33:50,999
Because if your gift is exhortation, write a card to somebody and exhort them, encourage

772
00:33:50,999 --> 00:33:52,679
them, lift them up.

773
00:33:52,679 --> 00:33:53,679
And I don't know.

774
00:33:53,679 --> 00:33:54,679
I never checked back.

775
00:33:54,679 --> 00:33:55,679
Did they do it?

776
00:33:55,679 --> 00:33:56,679
Did they use them?

777
00:33:56,679 --> 00:33:57,679
Did they go get their own cards?

778
00:33:57,679 --> 00:33:58,679
I don't know.

779
00:33:58,679 --> 00:33:59,679
But I'm trying to help them.

780
00:33:59,679 --> 00:34:02,199
Hey, here's, you've identified your gift.

781
00:34:02,199 --> 00:34:03,479
You want to develop that.

782
00:34:03,479 --> 00:34:05,119
Now use it.

783
00:34:05,119 --> 00:34:06,879
Use it for God's glory.

784
00:34:06,879 --> 00:34:07,879
Why?

785
00:34:07,879 --> 00:34:11,119
Because God gave it to you to be used.

786
00:34:11,119 --> 00:34:12,839
And so where is it to be used?

787
00:34:12,839 --> 00:34:15,239
It's to be used in the local church.

788
00:34:15,239 --> 00:34:17,719
So we look for those opportunities.

789
00:34:17,719 --> 00:34:19,599
You come to me as the pastor.

790
00:34:19,599 --> 00:34:24,839
You say, hey, I want to do, I want to use, and God's given me this gift and I want to

791
00:34:24,839 --> 00:34:27,399
be able to use this for God's glory.

792
00:34:27,399 --> 00:34:29,199
And what a blessing.

793
00:34:29,199 --> 00:34:35,399
I thank the Lord for those within our congregation that use their spiritual gifts to not only

794
00:34:35,399 --> 00:34:38,639
bring glory to God, but to edify the believers.

795
00:34:38,639 --> 00:34:40,399
And we make ourselves available.

796
00:34:40,399 --> 00:34:42,239
We seize the opportunities.

797
00:34:42,239 --> 00:34:43,239
Why?

798
00:34:43,239 --> 00:34:44,239
Because I want to use it.

799
00:34:44,239 --> 00:34:47,119
You know, it's really difficult for me.

800
00:34:47,119 --> 00:34:52,879
There's been times in which I've had super busy times and my schedule is seeming always

801
00:34:52,879 --> 00:34:53,919
busy.

802
00:34:53,919 --> 00:34:57,279
But someone, hey, will you preach this meeting or will you do this?

803
00:34:57,279 --> 00:34:58,279
It's hard for me to say no.

804
00:34:58,359 --> 00:34:59,359
Why?

805
00:34:59,359 --> 00:35:02,679
Because God gave me a gift and I want to be able to use it.

806
00:35:02,679 --> 00:35:07,399
Listen, I don't want to be in a place where we don't have church services because, well,

807
00:35:07,399 --> 00:35:11,639
you know, things are changing and we're just not having night services or this.

808
00:35:11,639 --> 00:35:15,459
No, I know so many people that are canceling church services and here we are adding one

809
00:35:15,459 --> 00:35:17,319
on Wednesday morning.

810
00:35:17,319 --> 00:35:23,039
It's a situation where what I'm saying is that when you know what it is and you've developed

811
00:35:23,039 --> 00:35:26,079
it, you ought to long to use it.

812
00:35:26,079 --> 00:35:27,199
It's not to be stored up.

813
00:35:27,199 --> 00:35:31,079
It's not something that we just kind of keep in a box somewhere.

814
00:35:31,079 --> 00:35:32,919
It's something that we use for God's glory.

815
00:35:32,919 --> 00:35:38,279
And when we do so, not only will God be glorified, not only will the believers be edified, but

816
00:35:38,279 --> 00:35:41,279
I truly believe this, you'll have joy.

817
00:35:41,279 --> 00:35:42,479
You'll have joy.

818
00:35:42,479 --> 00:35:47,159
We sing the song, there is joy in serving Jesus.

819
00:35:47,159 --> 00:35:49,519
It doesn't mean that it's not work.

820
00:35:49,519 --> 00:35:51,519
Serving the Lord is work.

821
00:35:51,519 --> 00:35:52,779
Amen?

822
00:35:52,779 --> 00:35:57,159
And some people have asked me over the years and some people that have taught and preached

823
00:35:58,119 --> 00:36:04,279
in my absence have commented on how challenging it is to, how can you develop so many messages

824
00:36:04,279 --> 00:36:06,759
a week, week after week after week?

825
00:36:06,759 --> 00:36:09,679
Listen, it's labor, but it's joy.

826
00:36:09,679 --> 00:36:10,839
I'm telling you, it's joy.

827
00:36:10,839 --> 00:36:13,279
I absolutely love it.

828
00:36:13,279 --> 00:36:14,399
Why?

829
00:36:14,399 --> 00:36:18,279
Because I know that this is what God equipped me to do.

830
00:36:18,279 --> 00:36:20,119
I know that it's what God gifted me to do.

831
00:36:20,119 --> 00:36:23,679
And I don't say that pridefully, I say that humbly, that to God be the glory.

832
00:36:23,679 --> 00:36:28,199
I want to do it for God's glory and I love doing it.

833
00:36:28,199 --> 00:36:29,199
Is it labor?

834
00:36:29,199 --> 00:36:30,199
Is it work?

835
00:36:30,199 --> 00:36:31,199
Absolutely.

836
00:36:31,199 --> 00:36:34,959
But I promise you, you'll have joy because there's joy in serving Jesus.

837
00:36:34,959 --> 00:36:40,959
We understand that the spiritual gifts as they've been described, defined in God's Word,

838
00:36:40,959 --> 00:36:45,039
and I say, I want to now discover what is my spiritual gift.

839
00:36:45,039 --> 00:36:46,359
And I want to develop this.

840
00:36:46,359 --> 00:36:47,359
Why?

841
00:36:47,359 --> 00:36:48,359
Because I want to use it.

842
00:36:48,359 --> 00:36:51,679
I want to be the best that I can be, not so that anyone would look at me and say, they

843
00:36:51,679 --> 00:36:52,679
should be lifted up.

844
00:36:52,679 --> 00:36:56,279
But also that people would say, this is God's grace.

845
00:36:56,279 --> 00:37:00,959
That God would be glorified and then deploy it, use it for God's glory.

846
00:37:00,959 --> 00:37:06,319
Look for those opportunities, seize those opportunities to be used for God's glory.

847
00:37:06,319 --> 00:37:07,319
Let's pray.

848
00:37:07,319 --> 00:37:08,359
Father, we love you.

849
00:37:08,359 --> 00:37:09,759
We thank you so much for loving us.

850
00:37:09,759 --> 00:37:15,119
We thank you for the spiritual gift, Lord, that you've given to each of us.

851
00:37:15,119 --> 00:37:16,799
We thank you for the truth of your Word.

852
00:37:16,799 --> 00:37:22,919
And I pray that you would help us as your people, Lord, to truly desire to know what

853
00:37:22,919 --> 00:37:25,959
our spiritual gift is, that God, you would reveal it to us.

854
00:37:25,959 --> 00:37:29,559
If maybe there's some here tonight that just don't know what their spiritual gift is, God,

855
00:37:29,559 --> 00:37:34,479
I pray that you would just lay upon their heart a desire to know it, Lord, to be able

856
00:37:34,479 --> 00:37:36,679
to discover what their spiritual gift is.

857
00:37:36,679 --> 00:37:40,239
Maybe there's some that know what their spiritual gift is, but they're just simply not using

858
00:37:40,239 --> 00:37:42,799
it, God, at this time for your glory.

859
00:37:42,799 --> 00:37:45,039
I pray that you'd stir us, Lord.

860
00:37:45,039 --> 00:37:51,199
Help us, even as Paul instructs Timothy, to stir up the gift that is in us, to rekindle,

861
00:37:51,199 --> 00:37:57,319
to redetermine that we will use the gift that you've bestowed upon us for your glory, that

862
00:37:57,319 --> 00:38:00,799
we would be good stewards of the manifold grace of God.

863
00:38:00,799 --> 00:38:04,199
I pray that in the moments of invitation that you'd have your will and way, that you would

864
00:38:04,199 --> 00:38:08,319
work in hearts and lives as only you can, and we'll thank you for it in Christ's name.

865
00:38:08,319 --> 00:38:09,319
We pray.

866
00:38:09,319 --> 00:38:09,319


